==English==

=== Pronunciation ===
heter-o-phone

plural: heterophones

===  noun  ===
'''heterophone'''
#{{Grammar}} (of a [[noun]]) two words that are spelled the same but have more than one pronounciation and meaning.

#{{Example}} '''desert''' - The excessive desert heat caused the officer to desert his post.


